Welcome to our weekly feature ✨#HauntedHotSpot✨, where we take a deeper look at some of the most famous (and famously terrifying) sites in the world. ⁠
⁠
This week’s pick: Lemp Mansion and Brewery ⁠
⁠
Now a restaurant and inn, the Lemp Mansion in St. Louis is marked by decades of tragedy for the wealthy Lemp family who originally lived there. At least four members of this doomed dynasty, owners of the Lemp Brewing Company, died in the house. Today, their spirits are said to linger, and the property is considered one of the most haunted in the country.⁠
⁠
You can stream #GhostAdventures' “Lemp Mansion and Brewery” now at the #linkinbio. #discoveryplus⁠
⁠
